quran[20{c,v,t}:
76,6,yeh aik behta chashma hoga jis ke pani ke sath Allah ke bande sharaab piyen ge aur jahan chahain ge بسہولت is ki shaakhen len ge
76,7,"yeh woh log hunge jo ( duniya mein ) Nazar poori karte hain, aur uss din se drtay hain jis ki aafat har taraf phaily hui hogi"
76,8,aur Allah ki mohabbat mein maskeen aur yateem aur qaidi ko khana khelate hain
76,9,"( aur unn se kehte hain ke ) hum tumhe sirf Allah ki khatir khula rahay hain, hum tum se nah koi badla chahtay hain nah shukriya"
76,10,hamein to apne Rab se uss din ke azaab ka khauf la-haq hai jo sakht museebat ka intahi taweel din hoga
76,11,pas Allah taala inhen uss din ke shar se bacha le ga aur inhen taazgee aur suroor bakhshay ga
76,12,aur unn ke sabr ke badlay mein unhen jannat aur reshmi libaas ataa karega
76,13,wahan woh onche masnadon par takiye lagaye baithy hunge nah unhen dhoop ki garmi sataye gi nah jaray ki thr
76,14,"jannat ki chaon un par jhuki hui saya kar rahi hogi, aur uss ke phal har waqt un ke bas mein hon ge ( ke jis terhan chahain inhen toar len )"
76,15,unn ke agay chandi ke bartan aur sheeshay ke pyaale gardish karaye ja rahay hunge
76,16,"sheeshay bhi woh jo chandi ki qisam ke hunge, aur un ko ( muntazmeen jannat ne ) theek andazay ke mutabiq bhara hoga"
76,17,un ko wahan aisi sharaab ke jaam pilaaye jayen ge jis mein sonth ki ameezash hogi
76,18,yeh jannat ka aik chashma hoga jisay Salsabeel kaha jata hai
76,19,un ki khidmat ke liye aisay larke dorrtay phir rahay hon ge jo hamesha larke hi rahen ge tum inhen dekho to samjhoo ke moti hain jo bekhair diye gay hain
76,20,wahan jidhar bhi tum nigah daalo ge naematain hi naematain aur aik barri saltanat ka sir o samaan tumhe nazar aeye ga
76,21,"unn ke oopar bareek resham ke sabz libaas aur Atlas o Deeba ke kapray hon ge, un ko chandi ke kangon pehna ye jayen ge, aur un ka Rab un ko nihayat pakeeza sharaab pilaaye ga"
76,22,yeh hai tumhari jaza aur tumhari kargzari qabil qader therihai
76,23,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum ne hi tum par yeh quran thora thora kar ke nazil kya hai"
76,24,"lehaza tum apne Rab ke hukum par sabr karo, aur inn mein se kisi bad amal ya munkir haq ki baat nah manu"
76,25,apne Rab ka naam subah o shaam yaad karo
